Package: aprgo
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, bluez, bluez-tools, adduser
Recommends: direwolf
Description: Self-contained APRS iGate, digipeater, and operator console
 aprgo is a single Go binary that owns the radio TNC (serial, Bluetooth, or
 TCP KISS), talks to APRS-IS, makes gating decisions, runs beacons, and serves
 a web console with interactive setup wizards. It replaces the aprx daemon
 plus a separate web UI with one process and one config file.
